OL,3,CNorthern Ireland teachers accept 5.5%
OL,4,Cpay offer
OL,6,FTeachers in Northern Ireland have
OL,7,Faccepted a new pay offer, removing the
OL,8,Fthreat of strike action in schools.
OL,10,FThe Northern Ireland Teachers' Council
OL,11,F(NITC), which represents the five main
OL,12,Funions in the sector, has accepted the
OL,13,F5.5% pay offer, ending ongoing
OL,14,Findustrial action.
OL,16,FTeachers had rejected previous offers
OL,17,Famid concerns over workload, and had
OL,18,Fbeen taking part in industrial action
OL,19,Fshort of strike action.
