OL,4,Cpay offer
OL,6,FSome of the unions had also voted in
OL,7,FDecember for strike action as part of
OL,8,Fthe ongoing dispute.
OL,10,FThe unions said there had now been a
OL,11,Fpersonal intervention by Education
OL,12,FMinister Paul Givan to address their
OL,13,Fconcerns.
OL,15,FAn independent review to cover all
OL,16,Faspects of workload has been
OL,17,Fcommissioned.
OL,19,FMr Givan said the end of industrial
OL,20,Faction "will increase stability in our
OL,21,Fschools".
