OL,6,FHe added: "The pay settlement will see
OL,7,Fthe starting salary for graduate
OL,8,Fteachers increasing to #31,650.
OL,10,F"This is an increase of #1,650 over
OL,11,Fthe year and it follows on from the
OL,12,Fteachers' pay settlement in April 2024
OL,13,Fwhich saw the starting salary for
OL,14,Fteachers raised by almost 25%.
OL,16,F"New teachers are now being paid
OL,17,F#7,513 more than the salary paid prior
OL,18,Fto the Executive returning last year."
