OL,6,FIt is anticipated that the pay
OL,7,Fincrease will be applied to most
OL,8,Fteachers in May and a full-time
OL,9,Fteacher on the starting salary would
OL,10,Freceive #1,237.50 in back pay for the
OL,11,Fperiod from September 1 2024 to May 31
OL,12,F2025, while a full-time teacher on
OL,13,Fupper pay scale point 3 would receive
OL,14,F#1,913.25.
OL,16,FMr Givan added: "Constructive
OL,17,Fnegotiations have taken place with
OL,18,Ftrade unions and I have listened to
OL,19,Ftheir concerns about workload.
