OL,6,F"I want to make meaningful progress on
OL,7,Fthe issues to ensure that teachers
OL,8,Fhave the time and space to focus on
OL,9,Fwhat matters most ` teaching, learning
OL,10,Fand supporting pupils in the classroom.
OL,12,F"In order to seek to break the
OL,13,Fdeadlock, I proposed a commission to
OL,14,Fconduct an independent review of all
OL,15,Faspects of workload, that will be
OL,16,Ftaken forward by a three-member panel,
OL,17,Fcomprising an independent chair
OL,18,Fappointed by me, a member nominated by
OL,19,Fthe unions and a member nominated by
OL,20,Fmanagement side.
