OL,6,F"The panel will examine workload and
OL,7,Freport to me by the end of November."
OL,9,FJacquie White, the chairwoman of NITC
OL,10,Fsaid it was a "significant first step"
OL,11,Fin delivering tangible change for the
OL,12,Fteaching profession.
OL,14,FShe added: "All parties involved ` the
OL,15,Fminister, the employers and the
OL,16,Fteaching unions ` are now committed to
OL,17,Faddressing the concerns which have
OL,18,Fbeen raised by teachers and school
OL,19,Fleaders over a considerable period of
OL,20,Ftime.
